 justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 4 n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t, l\u0103n x\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i, ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u hay ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 sau hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00e1c CLB \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1n tri\u1ec7t cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u cao th\u01b0\u1ee3ng, fair-play, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1t k\u00e9o kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. T\u1edbi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec1u s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadn ch\u1eadt k\u00edn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a V-League v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a &lsquo;ngu\u1ed9i&rsquo; v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat NHM t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung diem nhan chu y sau vong 4 V-League 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ch\u00fa \u00fd sau v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/Nhung-diem-nhan-chu-y-sau-vong-4-V-League-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018 di\u1ec5n ra h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng t\u0103ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn 25 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i r\u00fat ra. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &lsquo;s\u1ea1ch th\u1ebb&rsquo; l\u00e0 CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i va ch\u1ea1m l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB TP.HCM c\u1ee7a HLV Miura \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi 6 t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o Quang Nam, &nbsp;Ng\u1ecdc Th\u1ecbnh, Thanh Di\u1ec7p, Minh Trung, Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ea3i Anh. Trong khi Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u0169ng c\u00f3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb sau c\u00e1c h\u00e0nh vi ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng 4 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League 2018</span> \u0111\u00e3 ghi nh\u1eadn 58 ngh\u00ecn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u theo b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u1eeb ban qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a 7 SV\u0110 tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, s\u00e2n Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00f3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V v\u00e0o s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi 11 ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, &lsquo;th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n&rsquo; B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 x\u1ee9 Thanh t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c C\u0110V SLNA c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3n ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng x\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Thanh H\u00f3a c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SLNA cung tao ra nhieu co hoi nguy hiem khien Bui Tien Dung phai tro tai.\" title=\"SLNA c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m khi\u1ebfn B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/IMG_7556.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u00e2n Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u1eadt k\u00edn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 b\u1edfi s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a&nbsp;B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi Thanh H\u00f3a v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n l\u00e0 CLB HAGL. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n 10 ngh\u00ecn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 s\u00e2n Pleiku t\u1ed1i qua ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a NHM tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e2n L\u1ea1ch Tray \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ghi nh\u1eadn 8 ngh\u00ecn C\u0110V t\u1edbi c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 20 ngh\u00ecn \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 2 V-League, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V t\u1edbi s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 2, NHM H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu t\u1edbi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 xem HAGL, h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp l\u1eeda cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/guc-nga-truoc-thanh-hoa-hlv-slna-do-loi-cho-ong-park-hang-seo-168-183329.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/guc-nga-truoc-thanh-hoa-hlv-slna-do-loi-cho-ong-park-hang-seo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/guc-nga-truoc-thanh-hoa-hlv-slna-do-loi-cho-ong-park-hang-seo-168-183329.html\">G\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Thanh H\u00f3a, HLV SLNA \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c SLNA th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Thanh H\u00f3a l\u00e0 v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t do...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1n kh\u00e1t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1m d\u1ee9t sau khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-binh-duong-vs-ha-noi-17h00-ngay-14-vleague-2018-372-183304.html\" target=\"_blank\"> ghi b\u00e0n </span>trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 leo l\u00ean nh\u00f3m gi\u1eefa BXH v\u1edbi 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 4 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh Duc ghi ban thang dau tien o V-League\" title=\"Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf V-League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/sau-vong-4-vleague-2018-nhung-chien-thang-an-tuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf V-League 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh. V\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat qu\u00ea Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 g\u00f3p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 V-League 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SHB Da Nang thang nghet tho Sai Gon FC - Anh: CLB bong da Da Nang\" title=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC - \u1ea2nh: CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/shb-da-nang-32-sai-gon-chien-thang-nghet-tho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>6. Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00e2m nguy<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 sau 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Sau 4 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 \u0111ang \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 trong tay 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. C\u0169ng trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh v\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u00e0 SLNA khi c\u0169ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c th\u00ec t\u00e2n binh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 lo ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t. L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ecfng, thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn V-League v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ngo\u1ea1i binh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3</em> x<em>em L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u V-League v\u00e0 BXH V-League 2018</em>&nbsp;<strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/lich-thi-dau-25.html\" target=\"_blank\">t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</span></strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight HAGL 3-2 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018)</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/Highlight-HAGL-vs-Nam-Dinh-vong-4-vleague.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;\" times=\"\" new=\"\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-4-vleague-2018-nhung-chien-thang-an-tuong-168-183354.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/sau-vong-4-vleague-2018-nhung-chien-thang-an-tuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-4-vleague-2018-nhung-chien-thang-an-tuong-168-183354.html\">Sau v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018: Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nLo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018 di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/4 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u thuy\u1ebft...</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"715","checkdouble":"183357"},{"date":"06:56 02/04","title":"B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/bau-duc-noi-khong-voi-viec-tro-thanh-chu-tich-vff.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src: