e=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bau Duc noi khong voi viec tro thanh chu tich VFF hinh anh\" title=\"B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/Bau-Duc-noi-khong-voi-viec-tro-thanh-chu-tich-VFF-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eed tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi VFF. Tuy v\u1eady, sau khi Ti\u1ec3u ban Nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 VFF th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eed b\u1ed5 sung t\u1edbi h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 31/3, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eed \u00f4ng v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF kh\u00f3a m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eed v\u00e0o ch\u1ee9c danh Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecf ra b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n v\u00e0 v\u1eabn gi\u1eef v\u1eefng l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i VFF nhi\u1ec7m k\u1ef3 m\u1edbi. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau ch\u00ed h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia Ban ch\u1ea5p h\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m k\u1ef3 VIII l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 \u1edf kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y th\u00ec b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a VFF.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i VFF nhi\u1ec7m k\u1ef3 VIII s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 4/2018. Cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/5-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-hagl-32-nam-dinh-168-183338.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/5-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-hagl-32-nam-dinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/5-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-hagl-32-nam-dinh-168-183338.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-2 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL...</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"714","checkdouble":"183358"},{"date":"07:17 02/04","title":"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 4 V-League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/trong-tai-tiep-tuc-la-chu-de-gay-tranh-