orner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng 4 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00ec b\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup 2018 b\u1eb1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Bongda24h \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 AFF Cup 2018 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 Chanathip Songkrasin, Teerasil Dangda, Theerathon Bunmathan v\u00e0 Kawin Thamsatchanan\u00a0do \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m AFF Cup di\u1ec5n ra c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u00e1c CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vang 4 tru cot, DT Thai Lan van lam dieu nay de vo dich AFF Cup  hinh anh\" title=\"V\u1eafng 4 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eabn l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/12/18/Vo-dich-AFF-Cup,-Kiatisuk-mo-den-dang-cap-Chau-A-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd \u0111i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Milovan Rajevac\u00a0\u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ra tr\u1eddi T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, n\u00e2ng cao tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9. <o:p></o:p>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \"\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1eed s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c Th\u00e1i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo HLV\u00a0Milovan Rajevac, \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Tristan \u0110\u1ed7. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 'Th\u00e1i ki\u1ec1u' ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho \u0110TQG nh\u1eb1m chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Asian Cup v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 World Cup trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2017, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m HLV Kiatisak v\u1eabn c\u00f2n t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i AFF Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 8/11 \u0111\u1ebfn 15/12/2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a 10 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia v\u00e0o 2 b\u1ea3ng, m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng 5 \u0111\u1ed9i. N\u0103m nay \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng s\u1ed1 1. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho c\u1ea3 hai theo th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 4 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf nh\u00f3m 3, 5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi Th\u00e1i Lan, h\u1ecd \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng khu v\u1ef1c trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng AFF Cup 2018 sau 10 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><em>Video: B\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan (AFF Cup 2008)</em></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2015/10/13/cvluotve-1418634200080-08159.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"712","checkdouble":"183361"},{"date":"07:15 02/04","title":"Atletico Madrid 1-0 Deportivo: Ki\u00ean tr\u00ec b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/2/atletico-madrid-10-deportivo-kien-tri-bam-duoi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f