erelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u1edd pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kevin Gameiro tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Deportivo 1-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 30 La Liga 2017/18, qua \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eeba c\u1eaft \u0111u\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid v\u1eeba thu h\u1eb9p c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Barcelona.</strong><br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n<br>\r\nAtletico: Gameiro (34' pen)\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/2/yk5xe.MP4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Deportivo tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Wanda Metropolitano, Atletico quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hi v\u1ecdng b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Barcelona - \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Sevilla c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady, Atletico ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. V\u00e0 sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Diego Simeone \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 th\u1ebf qu\u00e2n b\u00ecnh \u1edf ph\u00fat 34, nh\u1edd c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kevin Gameiro. 1-0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSang hi\u1ec7p 2, th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Atletico. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 1, Rojiblancos kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ham t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i ch\u1eadm ch\u1eafc nh\u1eb1m b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t mong manh.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua Atletico Madrid vs Deportivo 1-0 tuong thuat La Liga 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Atletico Madrid vs Deportivo 1-0 t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt La Liga 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/tong-hop-atletico-madrid-10-deportivo-vong-30-la-liga-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gameiro ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11 m\u00e9t</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Deportivo s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n, song c\u00e1c pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch ho\u1eb7c thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn th\u00e9p m\u00e0 ph\u00eda Atletico t\u1ea1o ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChung cu\u1ed9c, Atletico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Deportivo 1-0 v\u1edbi pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Gameiro. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Madrid v\u1eeba c\u1eaft \u0111u\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 l\u00e0 Real Madrid, v\u1eeba thu h\u1eb9p c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Barca. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Atletico \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf t\u00fai 64 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i La Liga 2017/18, k\u00e9m g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalan 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 h\u01a1n K\u1ec1n K\u1ec1n Tr\u1eafng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n<br>\r\nAtletico: Oblak, Godin, Savic, Hern\u00e1ndez, Munoz (Costa 60'), Gabi, Saul, Koke, Partey (Moya 88'), Gameiro (Torres 72'), Correa<br>\r\nDeportivo: Ruben, Sidnei, Luisinho, Juanfran, Albentosa, Muntari (Valle 63'), Mosquera, Guilherme, Colak (Bakkali 77'), Adrian (Andone 82'), Perez</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"711","checkdouble":"183359"},{"date":"02:26 02/04","title":"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm, Wenger v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/thang-dam-wenger-van-khong-hai-long-ve-mot-dieu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;f