}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Wenger kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec7 Arsenal, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Stoke \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 \u1edf trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u1edf n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u1ede hi\u1ec7p 2 th\u00ec kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u00ec sao t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 l\u00e0 0-0, nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 3-0.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Arsenal v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o Top 4 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\">Europa League</span> \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tinh th\u1ea7n cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi CSKA Moscow v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wenger kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Arsenal \u1edf trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" title=\"Arsenal 3-1 Stoke\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/thang-dam-wenger-van-khong-hai-long-ve-mot-dieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wenger kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Arsenal \u1edf trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. HLV Arsene Wenger cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u1eebng lo, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m L\u1ec5 Ph\u1ee5c sinh di\u1ec5n ra, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd (ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9) c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh-c172-p1.html\">Premier League</span>, b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u00ecn chung \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng trong 2-3 tu\u1ea7n qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Arsene Wenger k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. B\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Stoke, HLV Wenger kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Arsenal-4.html\">Arsenal</span> l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265133\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/01/highlight-arsenal-vs-stoke-vong-32-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Arsenal vs Stoke\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Stoke\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Arsenal-vs-Stoke.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Stoke</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/11830354/013100\">Arsenal 3-0 Stoke<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-30-stoke-3-diem-khong-thuyet-phuc-172-183345.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/du-am-arsenal-30-stoke-3-diem-khong-thuyet-phuc.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-30-stoke-3-diem-khong-thuyet-phuc-172-183345.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal 3-0 Stoke: 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Stoke chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"710","checkdouble":"183348"},{"date":"02:55 02/04","title":"Hi\u1