u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. Trong \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/pierre-emerick-aubameyang-44233.html\">bom t\u1ea5n Aubameyang</span> l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e1c, Lacazette c\u0169ng g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn, Arsene Wenger t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t m\u1edbi, d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm. \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cV\u00e2ng, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nhau. Aubameyang \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, t\u1ea1i Saint-Etienne.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c2 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi Lewandowski \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/borussia-dortmund-62.html\">Dortmund</span>, Aubameyang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh. Ch\u1ec9 khi Lewandowski t\u1edbi Bayern Munich, anh \u1ea5y m\u1edbi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm \u1edf Dormund\u201d \u2013 Arsene Wenger l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal 3-0 Stoke Giao su ca ngoi song sat Laca-meyang  hinh anh\" title=\"Arsenal 3-0 Stoke Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0 ca ng\u1ee3i song s\u00e1t Laca-meyang  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/hiep-2-bung-no-giao-su-ca-ngoi-song-sat-lacameyang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Song s\u00e1t Lacazette - Aubameyang trong tr\u1eadn Arsenal 3-0 Stoke</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, sau khi Aubameyang quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/alexandre-lacazette-44374.html\">Lacazette</span>, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng: \u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0o ph\u00f3ng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi anh ta l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, b\u1edfi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean, Lacazette \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Thierry Henry t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\">Arsenal</span> cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cV\u1edbi t\u00f4i, Aubameyang \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf b\u00ean tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 Lacazette \u1edf v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\">Europa League</span> t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Alexandre Lacazette ra s\u00e2n, b\u1edfi Aubameyang kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec su\u1ea5t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh cho Mkhitaryan. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V vui l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi song s\u00e1t n\u00e0y, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-30-stoke-3-diem-khong-thuyet-phuc-172-183345.html\">Arsenal 3-0 Stoke</span> m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265133\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/04/01/highlight-arsenal-vs-stoke-vong-32-nha.mp4&autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Arsenal vs Stoke\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Stoke\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Arsenal-vs-Stoke.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Stoke</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/11830354/013100\">Arsenal 3-0 Stoke<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thang-dam-wenger-van-khong-hai-long-ve-mot-dieu-172-183348.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/thang-dam-wenger-van-khong-hai-long-ve-mot-dieu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thang-dam-wenger-van-khong-hai-long-ve-mot-dieu-172-183348.html\">Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm, Wenger v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span><br>\r\nWenger kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec7 Arsenal, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"709","checkdouble":"183349"},{"date":"02:28 02/04","title":"H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p Chelsea ngay t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge, Pochettino n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/ha-dep-chelsea-ngay-tai-stamford-bridge-pochettino-noi-gi.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWe