u1ee5c di\u1ec7n Top 4 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino phat bieu gi sau tran Chelsea vs Tottenham hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/HLV-Pochettino-phat-bieu-gi-sau-tran-Chelsea-vs-Tottenham-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea 3-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nChelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Morata, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Tottenham v\u00f9ng l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd l\u00e0 ghi li\u1ec1n&nbsp;3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Dele Alli \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, b\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Tottenham gi\u00fap Spurs n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m, &ldquo;G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng&rdquo; \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o Top 4 Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-tin-noi-sau-that-bai-cua-chelsea-truoc-tottenham-172-183343.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tottenham \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea</strong></span> tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u1edf k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Tottenham, \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi Spurs \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i The Blues ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge: &ldquo;H\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tottenham \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0o Top 3 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino phat bieu sau tran Chelsea vs Tottenham\" title=\"Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/pochettino.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;Sau 28 n\u0103m ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Chelsea </strong></span>\u1edf Stamford Bridge, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nao n\u00fang sau khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eb1ng Tottenham x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo;, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPochettino n\u00f3i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Dele Alli: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 21, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn v\u00e0 Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. T\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Alli s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m n\u1eefa&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVideo Chesea&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265159\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/01/highlight-chelsea-vs-tottenham-vong-32-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</di