strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 30, tuy nhi\u00ean ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a The Blues. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Dele Alli, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Eriksen \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\">Chelsea</span> ngay t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;<strong>T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t</strong>. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2 ho\u1eb7c 3-0, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua \u1edf ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7p 1, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p 2 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1ng, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m. B\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3 c\u0169ng v\u1eady, l\u1ebd ra b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn nh\u01b0 tr\u1eddi tr\u1ed3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Conte vs Chelsea 1-3 Tottenham\" title=\"Conte vs Chelsea 1-3 Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/thua-nguoc-spurs-conte-thua-nhan-chelsea-xung-dang-thu-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3. Gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. <strong>T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</strong> T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng v\u1eady, trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng v\u1eady, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u1edf trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\">Cup C1</span> hay kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf r\u1eb1ng, c\u00e1c CLB ph\u00eda tr\u00ean \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhanh. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Tottenham, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1eb7c kh\u00e1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. B\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 Champions League. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&rdquo; &ndash; Conte k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o Top 4, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/conte-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-va-pochettino-thay-the-172-183306.html\">Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte</span> l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265159\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/01/highlight-chelsea-vs-tottenham-vong-32-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Chelsea vs Tottenham\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Chelsea-vs-Tottenham.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Tottenham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ha-dep-chelsea-ngay-tai-stamford-bridge-pochettino-noi-gi-172-183350.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/ha-dep-chelsea-ngay-tai-stamford-bridge-pochettino-noi-gi.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ha-dep-chelsea-ngay-tai-stamford-bridge-pochettino-noi-gi-172-183350.html\">H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p Chelsea ngay t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge, Pochettino n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nHLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Tottenham, \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t 