u\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Pochettino t\u1ecf ra vui m\u1eebng th\u00ec Conte \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 28 n\u0103m Tottenham m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Chelsea, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh g\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. HLV Pochettino kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t, Harry Kane ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n khi Alvaro Morata m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 30, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Chelsea vs Tottenham Thien duong va dia nguc hinh anh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Chelsea vs Tottenham Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/Du-am-Chelsea-vs-Tottenham-Thien-duong-va-dia-nguc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea 3-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Dele Alli c\u00f9ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen gi\u00fap Tottenham ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 3-1. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Tottenham, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 12 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng 7 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Chelsea d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn 14 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 4 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 1 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDele Alli v\u00e0 Andreas Christensen, nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Pochettino v\u00e0 Conte c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. Alli trong tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 100 \u1edf Premier League \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 trong v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 4 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 c\u00e0ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n khi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i ghi 2 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2017 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Chelsea trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n White Hart Lane.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea 1-3 Tottenham man bao thu thanh cong cua Pochettino\" title=\"Chelsea 1-3 Tottenham m\u00e0n b\u00e1o th\u00f9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Pochettino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/chelsea-13-tottenham-man-tra-thu-ngot-ngao-cua-pochettino.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge sau 28 n\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Alli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/andreas-christensen-54231.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Christensen</strong></span> l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf 2/3 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. \u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1 c\u1ee7a Alli, anh m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed khi \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Caballero trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t, 4 ph\u00fat sau l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 27 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 theo k\u00e8m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Dele Alli, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mang v\u1ec1 cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Tottenham ch\u01a1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft th\u00ec nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda&nbsp;Chelsea t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 u\u1ec3 o\u1ea3i, b\u1ebf t\u1eafc ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Eden Hazard ch\u01a1i v\u1eadt v\u1edd trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Morata ngo\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ghi b\u00e0n th\u00ec x\u1eed l\u00fd v\u1ee5ng v\u1ec1, tranh ch\u1ea5p k\u00e9m. Willian c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Pochettino gi\u00fap Tottenham ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Conte t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-chelsea-vs-tottenham-tran-dau-vong-32-ngoai-hang-anh-201718-172-183331.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea 3-1</strong></span>, Spurs \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 25 tr\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 to\u00e0n h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua m\u1ed7i khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1990.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Chelsea vs Tottenham gi\u00fap Spurs ti\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0i trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o Top 4. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap &ldquo;G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng&rdquo; ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 v\u1edbi 64 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o Top 3 n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f9. Trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, duy nh\u1ea5t Man City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Spurs r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. V\u1edbi 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Chelsea v\u00e0 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n&nbsp;Arsenal, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pochettino \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea dau hang trong cuoc dua vao Top 4\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o Top 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-tin-noi-sau-that-bai-cua-chelsea-truoc-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Chelsea vs Tottenham \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o Top 4</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham gi\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u00e0o tham v\u1ecdng Top 4 c\u1ee7a Chelsea. H\u1ecd \u0111ang b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. The Blues \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5, k\u00e9m 2 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 8 v\u00e0 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea</strong></span> k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng trong Top 4 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t gi\u1eadn d\u1eef sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Chelsea c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00e0n ly. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a HLV Conte \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Tottenham<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Chelsea vs Tottenham\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Chelsea-vs-Tottenham.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nVideo Chelsea 1-3 Tottenham (V\u00f2ng 32 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265159\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/01/highlight-chelsea-vs-tottenham-vong-32-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"706","checkdouble":"183352"},{"date":"21:58 01/04","title":"TPHCM 1-0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: Phi S\u01a1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang v\u1ec1 ni\u1ec1m vui cho th\u1ea7y Miura","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/1/tphcm-10-khanh-hoa-phi-son-tiep-tuc-mang-ve-niem-vui-cho-thay-miura.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;