1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 T\u0129nh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho TP.HCM. Kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian sau \u0111\u00f3, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eb1ng co nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sanna.KH v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c 1-0, HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng CLB TP.HCM \u1edf V.League. C\u0169ng nh\u1edd v\u1eady m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean n\u1eeda tr\u00ean BXH V.League sau v\u00f2ng 4. </div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"705","checkdouble":"183335"},{"date":"19:37 01/04","title":"Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 3-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch thua tan n\u00e1t \u1edf C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/quang-ninh-30-quang-nam-nha-vo-dich-thua-tan-nat-o-cam-pha.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right