widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Mihail t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 1/4, hai CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn derby B\u1eafc Trung B\u1ed9 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ec9nh Thanh H\u00f3a. V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n l\u00e9p v\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb SLNA trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Thanh H\u00f3a thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0103n mi\u1ebfng tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o nguy hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"FLC Thanh Hoa 1-0 SLNA HLV Mihail chi ra van de cua Thanh Hoa hinh anh\" title=\"FLC Thanh H\u00f3a 1-0 SLNA HLV Mihail ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/FLC-Thanh-Hoa-1-0-SLNA-HLV-Mihail-chi-ra-van-de-cua-Thanh-Hoa-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh (tr\u00e1i) thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn FLC Thanh H\u00f3a 1-0 SLNA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 10 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ngo\u1ea1i binh Ofere \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Marian Mihail c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui sau khi Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0110inh Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 V\u0103n B\u00ecnh l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u0103n B\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00ean th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o, tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p TP.HCM. Ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn SLNA c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2\u201d. \u00a0<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-thanh-hoa-vs-slna-17h00-ngay-14-vleague-2018-372-183305.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/ket-qua-thanh-hoa-vs-slna-tran-dau-vong-4-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-thanh-hoa-vs-slna-17h00-ngay-14-vleague-2018-372-183305.html\">Thanh H\u00f3a 1-0 SLNA (KT): H\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u01b0ng ngh\u00e8o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ofere gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Marian Mihail \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng 1-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 4 NutiCafe V-League 2018 chi\u1ec1u 1/4.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ngo\u1ea1i binh, \u00f4ng Mihail n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i Omar \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Uche, h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0103n \u00fd v\u00e0 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, Uche lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 mang b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean n\u0103m nay Omar ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n Ofere ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi m\u1edbi sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hai h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft kh\u00e2u ghi b\u00e0n\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV FLC Thanh Hoa\" title=\"HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/HLV-FLC-Thanh-Hoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a cho r\u1eb1ng Minh Tu\u1ea5n c\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh V\u0169 Minh Tu\u1ea5n, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Romania \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y Minh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tuy nhi\u00ean khi v\u1ec1 Thanh H\u00f3a, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Minh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb \u1ed1m n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean g\u1eedi l\u1eddi khen SLNA v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng AFC Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y n\u00e0y, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean Top \u0111\u1ea7u, trong khi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Ngh\u1ec7 An d\u1eadm ch\u00e2n \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League 2018</span>.<br>\r\n<em>Xem L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u V-League v\u00e0 BXH V-League 2018</em>\u00a0<strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/lich-thi-dau-25.html\" target=\"_blank\">t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</span></strong><br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nHighlight Thanh H\u00f3a 1-0 SLNA (V\u00f2ng 4 V-League)</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/Highlight-Thanh-Hoa-vs-SLNA-vong-4-vleague.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"703","checkdouble":"183324"},{"date":"21:48 01/04","title":"G\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Thanh H\u00f3a, HLV SLNA \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho \u00f4ng Park Han