ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 thua \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00e0 v\u1ec1, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 n\u00e0y khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m rung l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc l\u00f3e s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Ofere \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 1-0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Guc nga truoc Thanh Hoa, HLV SLNA do loi cho ong Park Hang Seo hinh anh\" title=\"G\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Thanh H\u00f3a, HLV SLNA \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/guc-nga-truoc-thanh-hoa-hlv-slna-do-loi-cho-ong-park-hang-seo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV SLNA ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1ea5t s\u1ee9c do ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0110TVN</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a SLNA t\u1ecf ra nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc. \u00d4ng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t do h\u1ecd v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh h\u00f4m nay thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng sung s\u1ee9c v\u00ec di chuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u00f3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, ngo\u00e0i hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean l\u00e0 Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc v\u00e0 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay nh\u01b0ng v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua g\u1ea7n 15 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Jordan v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\", HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb hao t\u1ed5n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u0169ng ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf V-League khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1eeba tham d\u1ef1 AFC Cup l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung \u1edf \u0110TQG. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \"C\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t 4 ng\u00e0y/tr\u1eadn. Ng\u00e0y 5/4, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp h\u01a1i b\u1ea5t c\u1eadp\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Thanh H\u00f3a, SLNA \u0111ang d\u1eadm ch\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00eda cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng V-League v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u1ecd r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA</strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/Highlight-Thanh-Hoa-vs-SLNA-vong-4-vleague.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-chi-ra-van-de-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-sau-tran-gap-slna-168-183324.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-chi-ra-van-de-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-sau-tran-gap-slna.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-chi-ra-van-de-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-sau-tran-gap-slna-168-183324.html\">HLV Mihail ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p SLNA</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Mihail t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh 