</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 to\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh v\u00e0 Huy To\u00e0n, SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC.</strong><br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n<br>\r\nSHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (45'), Huy To\u00e0n (59'), Christian (70') <br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: Qu\u1ed1c Long (65'), Ho\u00e0ng Thi\u00ean (84')\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/da-nang-3-2-sai-gon.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch S\u00e0i G\u00f2n trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 45, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Diogo, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi xoay ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00fat xa tung l\u01b0\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua tuong thuat SHB Da Nang vs Sai Gon 3-2 V-League 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 3-2 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/da-nang-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC - \u1ea2nh: CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi h\u01a1n. Ph\u00fat 59, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 V\u00f5 Huy To\u00e0n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. D\u00f9 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f3 b\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t khi Qu\u1ed1c Long th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf ph\u00fat 65 nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh sau \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 Louis Christian l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean. Nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng Thi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-3 chung cu\u1ed9c khi\u1ebfn S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC ch\u00ecm s\u00e2u d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1y BXH. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 4 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, khi gi\u00fap SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\nSHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: V\u0103n H\u01b0ng, V\u0103n Long, Anh Quang, Vi\u1ec7t Anh, Nh\u1eadt T\u00e2n (Huy To\u00e0n 45&rsquo;), Thanh H\u1ea3i (Merlo 89&rsquo;), Minh T\u00e2m, V\u0103n Th\u1eafng, Diogo Junior, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (Duy Lam 90&rsquo;+3), Christian.<br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: V\u0103n Phong, Qu\u1ed1c Long, Ti\u1ebfn Duy, Ho\u00e0ng Qu\u1ea3ng (V\u0103n Ng\u1ecd 79&rsquo;), Xu\u00e2n D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ho\u00e0ng Thi\u00ean, V\u0103n Tri\u1ec1n, Th\u00e0nh T\u00edn, H\u1eefu S\u01a1n, Da Sylva, Dugary.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"700","checkdouble":"183332"},{"date":"21:10 01/04","title":"Mbappe n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/1/mbappe-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-neymar-toi-real-madrid.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-co