order:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Vi\u1ec7c Gareth Bale c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Benzema bu\u1ed9c Los Blancos ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe noi gi truoc tin don Neymar toi Real Madrid hinh anh\" title=\"Mbappe n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/Mbappe-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-Neymar-toi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra 250 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/psg-104.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PSG</strong></span>. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c NHM \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u sao Barca c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/neymar-44369.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Neymar</strong></span> t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cNh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 suy \u0111o\u00e1n. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 Neymar th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi nhau, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u anh \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh anh \u1ea5y r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe len tieng truoc tin don Neymar toi Real Madrid\" title=\"Mbappe l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/mbappe-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-neymar-toi-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201c\u01afu ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Neymar l\u00e0 World Cup 2018, anh \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c, PSG v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n anh \u1ea5y trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Neymar r\u1eddi PSG, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i quan t\u00e2m l\u00e0 khi n\u00e0o anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d, Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb PSG sa th\u1ea3i, Mbappe c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y: \u201cKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG. BL\u0110 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Emery chia tay PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"699","checkdouble":"183323"},{"date":"20:53 01/04","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 01/04: Sao kh\u1ee7ng Atletico mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/12/diem-tin-toi-0104-sao-khung-atletico-muon-den-mu-hon-la-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-siz