text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 01/04.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sao kh\u1ee7ng Atletico mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin toi 0104 Sao khung Atletico muon den MU hon la Barca hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 0104 Sao kh\u1ee7ng Atletico mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/3/Diem-tin-toi-0104-Sao-khung-Atletico-muon-den-MU-hon-la-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Griezmann mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo Don Balon, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid \u01b0u ti\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Barca. Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>MU hy sinh Martial \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Bale</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>Theo Mirror, \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real Madrid nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Gareth Bale, M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Anthony Martial t\u1edbi Bernabeu theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Man \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ed9ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Real mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Morata</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>Theo Sunday Express, Real Madrid ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Benzema \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Barca c\u0169ng h\u1ecfi mua Salah</strong></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Barca c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mohamed Salah c\u1ee7a Liverpool, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lucas Hernandez</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport, Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ecfi mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lucas Hernandez c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Chelsea chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Newcastle</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Jamaal Lascelles\" title=\"Chelsea mua Jamaal Lascelles\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/chelsea-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-newcastle.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mua Jamaal Lascelles</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Newcastle nh\u1ea3 trung v\u1ec7 Jamaal Lascelles. Ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o &ldquo;Ch\u00edch ch\u00f2e&rdquo;, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm thay David Luiz c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Arsenal b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matthijs de Ligt</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Mirror, Arsenal \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Matthijs de Ligt c\u1ee7a Ajax, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 18 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Galatasaray mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u sao MU</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u01b0a tin Galatasaray mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Shinji Kagawa, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Dortmund, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Conte l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Conte la uu tien so mot cua PSG khi len ke hoach thay nguoi vao he nay. Anh: BPI.\" title=\"Conte l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a PSG khi l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u1ea2nh: BPI.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/psg-bi-mat-dam-phan-voi-conte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Conte l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Conte kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng do BL\u0110 Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, d\u00f9 \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i th\u00ec \u00f4ng v\u1eabn t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Tuchel t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Bayern Munich, HLV Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. C\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"698","checkdouble":"183326"},{"date":"20:20 01/04","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Arsenal vs Stoke tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 32 Premier League 2017/18","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/30/ket-qua-arsenal-vs-stoke-tran-dau-vong-32-premier-league-201718.png","ne