0f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tung ra nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u00e1p ng\u1ea3. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 4, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Shaqiri \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc trong gang t\u1ea5c. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 22, Arsenal t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u01b0ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Ramsey l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eadp x\u00e0 ngang b\u1eadt ra ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal khong tao ra nhung co hoi ro rang trong 45 phut thi dau dau tien\" title=\"Arsenal kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/arsenal.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng Arsenal ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng Elneny hay Aubameyang \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Arsenal c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 67%, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Stoke City c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. H\u00f2a 0-0 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 khi\u1ebfn di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Arsenal ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. Ph\u00fat 56, Welbeck tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 ngang. S\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ph\u00fat 75, Mesut Ozil b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong b\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 11m v\u00e0 Aubameyang d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cu dup cua Aubameyang va pha lap cong cua Lacazette giup Arsenal danh bai Stoke 3-0\" title=\"C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Aubameyang v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Lacazette gi\u00fap Arsenal \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Stoke 3-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/arsenal-4.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Aubameyang v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Lacazette gi\u00fap Arsenal \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Stoke 3-0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">10 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>Aubameyang v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ed3i n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 87, Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 11m khi Lacazette b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 11m \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi r\u00fat ng\u1eafn kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Top 4 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Arsenal: </strong>Ospina, Bellerin, Chambers, Mustafi, Monreal, Elneny (Xhaka, 76'), Wilshere (Mkhitaryan, 76'), Ramsey, Ozil, Welbeck (Lacazette, 61'), Aubameyang</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Stoke City:</strong> Butland, Johnson, Shawcross, Martins Indi, Pieters, Bauer, Ndiaye, Allen, Sobhi (Crouch, 80'), Diouf (Berahino, 61'), Shaqiri</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"697","checkdouble":"183318"}]}